  }, "Processes"), ". In terms of the functionality of Nextflow, this paradigm is really just a method of programming workflows \u2014 it doesn\u2019t in many cases grant users of Nextflow any new abilities to create workflows that couldn\u2019t be created with other tools. That is until we leverage the power of ", mdx("inlineCode", {
